---
// Home page hero. Positioning: "Network monitoring without the
// SolarWinds tax." Direct, comparative, punchy. Backed by three
// supporting points (no per-node, self-hosted, 10-min install).
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-b from-slate-50 to-white">
  <!-- Subtle grid background -->
  <div
    class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-[0.04]"
    style="background-image: linear-gradient(to right, #1e293b 1px, transparent 1px), linear-gradient(to bottom, #1e293b 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 32px 32px;"
    aria-hidden="true"
  ></div>

  <div class="container-wide pt-20 pb-24 sm:pt-28 sm:pb-32">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">For SMB and mid-market IT teams</p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold leading-[1.1] tracking-tight text-slate-900 sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl">
        Network monitoring without the
        <span class="relative whitespace-nowrap text-brand-600">
          SolarWinds tax
          <svg
            class="absolute -bottom-2 left-0 h-3 w-full text-accent-400"
            viewBox="0 0 200 12"
            fill="none"
            preserveAspectRatio="none"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path d="M2 9 Q50 2 100 6 T198 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" />
          </svg>
        </span>
        <span class="text-slate-900">.</span>
      </h1>

      <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-600 sm:text-xl">
        Self-hosted. Per-tier pricing — never per-node. SNMP, NetFlow, syslog,
        and Windows/Linux agents in one platform. Install in 10 minutes on
        a single Linux host.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:gap-4">
        <a href="/download" class="btn-primary">
          Start 30-day free trial
          <svg class="h-4 w-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
          </svg>
        </a>
        <a href="/pricing" class="btn-secondary">
          See pricing
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
        No credit card required. 10 fully-monitored devices + unlimited ICMP-only.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Trust strip — three quick-scan benefits -->
    <div class="mx-auto mt-20 grid max-w-4xl grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-100 text-brand-700">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">No per-node billing</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Flat tier-based annual pricing. Add devices freely without surprise
          quarterly true-ups.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-100 text-brand-700">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">Self-hosted</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Runs on your hardware. Your data stays in your network. No SaaS
          dependency, no surprise outages.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="mx-auto flex h-10 w-10 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-brand-100 text-brand-700">
          <svg class="h-5 w-5" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
          </svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="mt-3 text-base font-semibold text-slate-900">10-minute install</h3>
        <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">
          Docker Compose, two commands, you're at the bootstrap admin page.
          No Windows server required.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
